title: UltimateTorrentGrabber v1.0 gazza-911 [Bubanee]
description:
Ultimate Torrent Grabber 

Is a Google Chrome Extension

What it does is add an option in the right click menu upon highlighting a 40 Character Torrent Info_Hash

It will give you 3 choices, a Magnet with ready loaded popular public trackers and 2 Torrent Options Zoink and Torcache

Zoink and Torcache? 
These are where many sites store your uploaded .torrent file or you can manual load it yourself at either. 
Upon clicking Zoink or Torcache will give you a .torrent download. 

How to Install. 

Open up Google Chrome and Open Extensions 

chrome://extensions/

or use the tab up top right, tools > extensions 

Drag and drop the crx file on the open page. Thats it ! 

Idea by Bubanee, brains By gazza-911
